# Root env example — historical EVM/Foundry vars removed.
# Prefer per-package env files:
#   frontend/.env.local          + frontend/.dev.vars   (Vite + Pages Functions)
#   frontend/.env.example        + frontend/.dev.vars.example
#   relayer/.dev.vars            (CCTP + Base/ZeroDev cross-chain)
#   keeper/.dev.vars             (lifeboat radar)
#   deploy/.env                  (Oracle VM compose — relayer + radar + tunnel)
#
# Gas abstraction is NOT 1Shot. Stellar path uses STELLAR_RELAYER_SECRET
# (fee-bump). Base leg uses ZeroDev + RELAYER_BASE_PRIVKEY. See prd.md / GETTING_STARTED.md.

# Optional shared keys if a monorepo tool reads the root (otherwise leave empty):
# TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-...
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...
# ALLOWED_ORIGIN=https://your-app.pages.dev
